<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Votre panier vous attend — Andromeda Paris</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f0ede8;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#f0ede8;padding:40px 16px;">
  <tr><td align="center">
    <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;">

      <!-- HEADER -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#191a2e;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;padding:40px 48px 32px;text-align:center;">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1000/9375/5727/files/logo-blanc-andromeda.png?v=1774981994" alt="Andromeda Paris" height="36" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 24px;">
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid rgba(200,184,154,0.3);"></td></tr></table>
          <p style="color:#C8B89A;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:20px;font-weight:bold;">Votre panier vous attend</p>
          <h1 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:26px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.4;">
            Votre nuit parfaite<br><span style="font-weight:bold;">est à portée de main</span>
          </h1>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- BODY -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#ffffff;padding:40px 48px;">

          <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:32px;">
            {{ customer.first_name }}, vous avez laissé quelque chose dans votre panier. Votre masque de sommeil en soie de mûrier Grade 6A vous attend — et les stocks sont limités.
          </p>

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:32px;"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;"></td></tr></table>

          <p style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8B89A;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:20px;">Dans votre panier</p>

          {% for line in checkout.line_items %}
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f9f7f4;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">
            <tr><td style="padding:20px 24px;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td width="72" style="vertical-align:top;">
                    {% if line.image %}
                    <img src="{{ line.image | img_url: '64x64', crop: 'center' }}" alt="{{ line.title }}" width="64" height="64" style="border-radius:8px;display:block;">
                    {% else %}
                    <div style="width:64px;height:64px;background:#ebe8e3;border-radius:8px;"></div>
                    {% endif %}
                  </td>
                  <td style="padding-left:16px;vertical-align:top;">
                    <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;">{{ line.title }}</p>
                    {% if line.variant_title != 'Default Title' %}
                    <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:8px;">{{ line.variant_title }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    <p style="color:#C8B89A;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;">{{ line.price | money }}</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td></tr>
          </table>
          {% endfor %}

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:28px 0;"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;"></td></tr></table>

          <!-- Arguments -->
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
            <tr>
              <td width="33%" style="padding-right:8px;vertical-align:top;text-align:center;">
                <p style="color:#C8B89A;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px;">✦</p>
                <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;">Grade 6A</p>
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:11px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;">Soie de mûrier parmi les plus rares</p>
              </td>
              <td width="33%" style="padding:0 4px;vertical-align:top;text-align:center;">
                <p style="color:#C8B89A;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px;">✦</p>
                <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;">22 mommes</p>
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:11px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;">Grammage optimal pour la peau</p>
              </td>
              <td width="33%" style="padding-left:8px;vertical-align:top;text-align:center;">
                <p style="color:#C8B89A;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px;">✦</p>
                <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;">Livraison offerte</p>
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:11px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;">Dès votre première commande</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr><td align="center">
              <a href="{{ checkout.abandoned_checkout_url }}" style="display:inline-block;background:#191a2e;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:16px 40px;border-radius:4px;">
                Finaliser ma commande
              </a>
            </td></tr>
          </table>

        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- BANDE -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#f9f7f4;border-left:4px solid #C8B89A;padding:20px 48px;">
          <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;">
            ✦ &nbsp;Des questions avant de commander ? Répondez à cet email — notre équipe vous répond sous 24h.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#191a2e;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px;padding:32px 48px;text-align:center;">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1000/9375/5727/files/logo-blanc-andromeda.png?v=1774981994" alt="Andromeda Paris" height="24" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 20px;opacity:0.5;">
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;">
            Andromeda Paris — {{ shop.url }}<br>
            Des questions ? Répondez à cet email, nous sommes là pour vous.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:16px;">
            <a href="{{ shop.url }}/account" style="color:rgba(200,184,154,0.6);font-size:11px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:1px;">Se désabonner</a>
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr><td style="height:40px;"></td></tr>
    </table>
  </td></tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
